{"tid":498684,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]近年我有甩頭髮既煩惱....","createTime":"2017-12-14T04:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T05:15:37.000Z","uid":39131,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe4f1e65e5e7fd9a8f7a1e3341a1d3b0cd2fac2","tid":498684,"uid":39131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:59:55.000Z","msg":"利申中上樣<br />\n本身10年前gel起個頭都係個型男來<br />\n但係偏偏就有甩頭髮既煩惱<br />\n而且我係打份無前途但穩定既牛工(餐廳後勤清潔)<br />\n一日都係細個信錯人,淨係掛住做運動操fit自己以為可以出人投地,最後出到來只可以乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 橙過IT同晒銀時既朋友<br />\n今日有個某朋友帶多個fd來話叫我一齊轉行做運動員<br />\n我心諗我成世人波皮都無掂過毛端端踢乜野波<br />\n令到我最唔据係佢地咁樣衰,就無甩頭髮!!!!<br />\n我咁靚仔,就偏偏甩頭髮!!!!<br />\n<br />\n點解呢個世界咁唔公平!!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下有無巴打有生髮公司介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8697d70cf54e2f24649ac2d5955e30d81b7909","tid":498684,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:03:09.000Z","msg":"德國發現工程幫到你"},{"pid":"30e500541207ab2a60f81898e15e576ce217777a","tid":498684,"uid":39131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:06:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國發現工程幫到你</blockquote><br />\n真的嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見佢廣告好似好多咁<br />\n死喇死喇頭先啲洗潔精彈左上個頭到,唔知會唔會甩得更勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a4764d4ec2e4262e4c52f48a27fde9effeefce","tid":498684,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:07:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60e2525b6950f1a8ca8c4699629ba113bde35166","tid":498684,"uid":15224